Find out INSTANTLY the status of every slope for Ski or Snowboarding in Romania:
- UPDATED STATUS: up to date information about all open slopes in: Poiana Brasov, Predeal, Straja, Azuga, Busteni or any other domain in Romania;
- DIFFICULTY: the level of difficulty and dimension of each slope;
- WEATHER FORECAST: updated current weather and forecast, as well as snow level;
- LIVE WEBCAM: real time images directly from your favorite slope.

It has never been easier to have easy access to information about all slopes in Romania:
- save your favorite slopes in favorites list;
- get notifications when a slope has opened;
- have instant access to news about the slope you want to go to.

